Supported conversions : 


from ENRICH TEI(text/xml) format to FO(text/xml) format;

from ENRICH TEI(text/xml) format to ENRICH TEI(application/xhtml+xml) format;

from ENRICH TEI(text/xml) format to ENRICH TEI(application/x-latex) format;

from ENRICH TEI(text/xml) format to ENRICH TEI(application/msword) format;

from ENRICH TEI(application/msword) format to ENRICH TEI(text/xml) format;
